00:48:26.150 --> 00:48:27.650
Yeah, they build.

00:48:27.650 --> 00:48:28.030
RYAN GERMICK: Termites.

00:48:28.030 --> 00:48:29.530
RICH MOORE: Yeah.

00:48:29.530 --> 00:48:32.150
RYAN GERMICK: So if there are
