00:48:36.290 --> 00:48:38.100
AUDIENCE: How do you, from
a director's role--

00:48:38.100 --> 00:48:39.566
RICH MOORE: This is going
to be a hard one.

00:48:39.566 --> 00:48:39.920
I can tell.

00:48:39.920 --> 00:48:44.640
I can already tell this is going
to go for the throat.

00:48:44.640 --> 00:48:46.410
RYAN GERMICK: It's gonna
