01:02:06.870 --> 01:02:09.870
So now let's try something
that did work.

01:02:09.870 --> 01:02:13.180
And that's what we always tried
to do on this movie was

01:02:13.180 --> 01:02:16.460
to be wrong quickly.

01:02:16.460 --> 01:02:20.330
Let's just throw it out there
and see if it works.

01:02:20.330 --> 01:02:21.560
And if it doesn't, OK.

01:02:21.560 --> 01:02:24.730
We know what we're
shooting for.

01:02:24.730 --> 01:02:31.130
We knew early on in this movie
who our characters were, when

01:02:31.130 --> 01:02:34.060
Phil and I were designing the
characters and putting

01:02:34.060 --> 01:02:35.260
