01:02:35.260 --> 01:02:39.540
So we knew from a very early
point in the development of

01:02:39.540 --> 01:02:41.760
the film who those
characters were.

01:02:41.760 --> 01:02:45.820
And the story changed
quite a few times.

01:02:45.820 --> 01:02:50.490
