like that overnight.

01:03:04.455 --> 01:03:07.970
It takes time to kind of let
these things percolate.

01:03:07.970 --> 01:03:10.740
And the whole thing has an
organic feeling to it.

01:03:10.740 --> 01:03:13.290
It grows at its own
pace, I believe.

01:03:13.290 --> 01:03:19.540
I think things will happen
when they want to happen.

01:03:19.540 --> 01:03:22.480
Things will be solved when
they need to be solved.

01:03:22.480 --> 01:03:25.990
And for me, it's just being
patient enough to

01:03:25.990 --> 01:03:29.460
